OL,4,CDisadvantaged pupils fearful over exam
OL,5,Cgrades
OL,6, Many pupils from low-income families in
OL,7, the UK worry they will receive unfair
OL,8, grades this summer, a Social Mobility
OL,9, Foundation (SMF) survey suggests.
OL,11,FMore than half of them think they will
OL,12,Fbe unable to appeal, after teacher
OL,13,Fassessments replaced cancelled exams.
OL,15,FThe charity wants governments across
OL,16,Fthe UK to allow all pupils in the final
OL,17,Fyear of sixth form to repeat a year, if
OL,18,Ftheir schools approve.
OL,20,F"We cannot afford to get this wrong
OL,21,Fagain," said SMF chairman Alan Milburn.
